text: There are several places named Kilsyth: *Kilsyth, Scotland *Kilsyth, a suburb of Melbourne, Victoria, Australia *Electoral district of Kilsyth, a former electoral district in Victoria, Australia *Kilsyth, Ontario in Canada There are also 2 towns named Kilsyth in the United States. *Kilsyth, West Virginia *Kilsyth, Tennessee
